snippet.title: Finding Side Lengths of a Figure Given the Perimeter | Measurement and Algebra
snippet.description:
http://tapintoteenminds.com Math Tutorial "Quick Question Solution" involves a field in the shape of a trapezoid with a given perimeter of 460 m.  Students are to determine the dimensions of each side given expressions involving an unknown for each of the four sides.

Taken from EQAO Winter 2008 Open Response Quesiton
